data.description: ATTENTION HOMEBUYERS AND INVESTORS!!! Unlock your dreams of homeownership or expand your investment portfolio with our PRICE ADJUSTMENT. FANTASTIC LOCATION! This beautiful one-level pool home is situated in the desirable Lindfield's community. with 4 spacious bedrooms and 2 upgraded bathrooms. Countless modern updates have been made, such as fresh interior and exterior paint, exquisite tile flooring and thresholds throughout, a new pool heater, and an energy-efficient variable pool pump. The open living room and dining room, along with two dining areas, offer ample living space for your comfort. Step out to the rear of the property and discover a private pool enclosure, providing a perfect spot to relax and bask in the sunshine without any rear neighbors to disturb your tranquility. The air conditioning and split AC/heat, along with the insulated converted garage, ensure your utmost comfort in all seasons. This incredible home comes fully furnished or turnkey, making it an ideal option for short-term or long-term leasing or for a family seeking a beautiful, move-in ready residence. Best of all, there are no HOA restrictions, allowing you the freedom to enjoy this property as you wish. Equipped with convenient USB outlets, top-of-the-line smart TVs sized no less than 55 inches, a remarkable 120-inch movie theater, and a fun-filled play area, this home has everything you could ever desire. Showings will be scheduled based on availability. Don't miss out on this limited time offer.
